      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/51/1058",
      "text": [
        " اَلصَّلاَةِ قَالَ «نَعَمْ وَ إِنْ كَانَ بَيْنَكَ وَ بَيْنَ صَاحِبِكَ اَلْيَمُّ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1058 - Abu Basir said to him:\n\"I hear someone sneeze, and I praise Allah (swt) and send blessings upon the Prophet (sw) while I am in prayer.\"\nImam (as) said: \"Yes, even if there is a sea between you and your companion.\""
        ]
      }
    },
